# DCP Database Design

## Main Tables

### Users
- id
- username
- callsign
- email
- password_hash
- avatar
- created_at

### Devices
- id
- user_id
- device_name
- platform
- app_version

### Talk Groups
- id
- name
- description

### Messages
- id
- sender_id
- group_id
- message
- created_at

### Voice Sessions
- id
- user_id
- protocol
- duration
- started_at

### Protocols
- id
- name
- version
- plugin
